    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's called 'The Jewish in the Ghetto,' 'Jews in the Ghetto.' This picture, probably in Israel, I, I found it.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't-- I don't remember how it could-- how it turned out, how I found it and who gave it to me.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So now, this picture is very-- is not clear enough.",
      "recall": false,
      "topics": []
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I took it to a-- here in Staten Island to make a, a copy of it.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's how it came out, this--",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the picture, is my brother-- the big brother, Charlie, and the smaller brother, Nissy.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were-- they were-- they look like when they were young, when they were about a few years before they were taken to Kamenets-Podolskiy.",
