      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't remember the exact date when I did it, but it's about the postcard which I received in 1941 from my mother in Budapest during the war.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Parents"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is a photograph I did last year when I painted the portrait of Steven Spielberg.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I mailed it to-- I shipped it to him.",
      "recall": true,
      "topics": [
        "Other"
      ]
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he sent me a, a nice letter-- a thank-you letter for-- he liked it very much.",
      "recall": true,
